### 1. 新增患者
POST http://localhost:8081/patient/add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

{
  "realName": "李大爷",
  "age": 68,
  "gender": "男",
  "phone": "13900139000",
  "chronicType": "高血压,糖尿病",
  "address": "杭州市萧山区XX小区"
}

### 2. 修改患者
POST http://localhost:8081/patient/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

{
  "id": 1,
  "realName": "李建国",
  "age": 69
}

### 3. 删除单个患者
DELETE http://localhost:8081/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 4. 查询单个患者详情
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/1
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 5. 患者分页查询
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10&chronicType=高血压
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 6. 统计本人患者总数
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/count
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 【新增1】患者姓名下拉列表
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/list/name
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 【新增2】按慢病类型统计数量
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/count/by-type?chronicType=糖尿病
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 【新增3】本人患者平均年龄
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/age/avg
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 【新增4】年龄最大患者
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/oldest
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 【新增5】最近新增患者
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/latest
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

### 【新增6】批量删除患者
DELETE http://localhost:8081/patient/batch
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token

[2,3]

### 【新增7】手机号模糊查询患者
GET http://localhost:8081/patient/search/phone?phone=139
Authorization: Bearer 替换为登录拿到的token